  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 22",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.51,
      "endTime": 2.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "By heart",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.55,
      "endTime": 9.43
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Which actor read the letter in the end, the aristocrat or the gaoler?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.44,
      "endTime": 17.31
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Some plays are so successful that they run for years on end.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 17.32,
      "endTime": 22.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In many ways, this is unfortunate for the poor actors who are required to go on repeating the same lines night after night.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 22.41,
      "endTime": 32.96,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "One would expect them to know their parts by heart and never have cause to falter.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 32.97,
      "endTime": 39.11,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Yet this is not always the case.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.12,
      "endTime": 42.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A famous actor in a highly successful play was once cast in the role of an aristocrat who had been imprisoned in the Bastille for twenty years.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.81,
      "endTime": 54.24
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In the last act, a gaoler would always come on to the stage with a letter which he would hand to the prisoner.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 54.25,
      "endTime": 63.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Even though the noble was expected to read the letter at each performance, he always insisted that it should be written out in full.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 63.38,
      "endTime": 72.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "One night, the gaoler decided to play a joke on his colleague to find out if,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.81,
      "endTime": 78.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "after so many performances, he had managed to learn the contents of the letter by heart.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 78.41,
      "endTime": 85.44
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The curtain went up on the final act of the play and revealed the aristocrat sitting alone behind bars in his dark cell.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 85.45,
      "endTime": 95.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Just then, the gaoler appeared with the precious letter in his hands.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.16,
      "endTime": 100.54,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He entered the cell and presented the letter to the aristocrat.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.55,
      "endTime": 105.35
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But the copy he gave him had not been written out in full as usual.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.36,
      "endTime": 110.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It was simply a blank sheet of paper.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 110.5,
      "endTime": 114.13,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The gaoler looked on eagerly, anxious to see if his fellow actor had at last learnt his lines.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 114.14,
      "endTime": 122.22,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The noble stared at the blank sheet of paper for a few seconds.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 122.23,
      "endTime": 127.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Then, squinting his eyes, he said: 'The light is dim. Read the letter to me.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 127.45,
      "endTime": 136.03,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Me",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我（宾格）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "And he promptly handed the sheet of paper to the gaoler.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 136.04,
      "endTime": 140.48
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Finding that he could not remember a word of the letter either,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 140.49,
      "endTime": 144.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the gaoler replied: 'The light is indeed dim, sire.  I must get my glasses.  '",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.83,
      "endTime": 152.55,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "With this, he hurried off the stage.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 152.56,
      "endTime": 156.37,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Much to the aristocrat's amusement,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 156.38,
      "endTime": 158.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the gaoler returned a few moments later with a pair of glasses and the usual copy of the letter which he proceeded to read to the prisoner.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 158.83,
      "endTime": 163.83
    }
  ]
}
